<h2>Assignment 3: Roshambo</h2>

<ul>
<li><a href="as3.html">Specifications</a>
<li>Sample executables are in <tt>/u/csc209h/fall/pub/a3</tt> on CDF.
These programs print diagnostic information to <tt>stderr</tt>, which
your final programs should not do!
<li>To eliminate the debugging ouput from the
sample programs, redirect the <tt>stderr</tt> to
<tt>/dev/null</tt>.
For example (under <tt>sh</tt> or <tt>bash</tt> only),<br>
<tt>$ ./roshambo.sample rps0 rps0 2&gt; /dev/null</tt><br>
Your output should look like this result.
<li>To make symbolic links to the sample programs in your working
directory, use the command<br>
<tt>ln -s /u/csc209h/fall/pub/a3/{roshambo.sample,rps0} .</tt>
<li><a href="as3pt3.html">Part 3</a> (optional, for A3 bonus marks)
<li><a href="http://www.cdf.utoronto.ca/~csc209h/fall/tournament/">Tournament results</a>
